Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing? Cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck did you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made Judy's meals every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.59,0:00:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I took one of the more expensive pots from the shelf,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thrust a 50-dollar bill at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pops at the store dropped his jaw! His face was so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:00:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:01:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you're saying that you want to train that girl as an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.90,0:01:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.05,0:01:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how to fire a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.26,0:01:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you feel lucky, punk?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Clint Eastwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.75,0:01:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be more precise, I'm talking about something to do with avenging Judy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you straight. Five million isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the shortfall is small enough... that you can earn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be my assistant for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing! This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll be an assistant to Phantom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming your assistant means...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I can be by your side when you avenge Judy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, there's something we have to pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go buy some tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've got a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by at our hideout today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work is boring. It's not fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay put and wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five million dollars was stolen and four of our men were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, it was on your turf.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that, you're saying that there's no apology or compensation from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for those who died,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we can't be responsible for what happened before the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muroto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it is true that our business was interfered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're currently doing everything we can to find out what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I sure hope you'll be able to get the money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the matter, that included, is resolved, I'd like you to stay in LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'll promise you a comfortable stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:04:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our money was stolen. Our men were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't shamelessly go back to Japan empty handed anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Shiga. Why don't we extend our vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we going to tell the old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him the water disagreed with me or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ringleader is Isaac Wisemel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wisemel is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no trace that the information on the deal was leaked to the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an inside job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this case hurt Wisemel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that no one would think
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he'd cause trouble in his own backyard for only five million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a perfect guise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wisemel's goal is to interfere with the Godo Family's joining Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably doesn't like me getting a big backing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way it was carried out was too aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think he got to being a senior member with just his tough talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a man who uses force to get his way when necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll go after Godo again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you let him go back to Japan and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work without a bait, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go shark fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Godo is the bait and you're the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's been decided that we're going to stay here longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay here a little longer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the contingency plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boring talk can wait. It spoils the alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you have a wonderful vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a coordinator we were finally able to track down
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who has no connections to Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giuseppe, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His sales pitch was that he's well versed in the underworld. If that's really true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't have to plan everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it and just have a drink. It's on Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is 30 year old liquor, Mr. Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bait... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideout is secure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this also part of that "comfortable stay" you mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I was serious when I said I wouldn't go back empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you've got a subordinate who isn't happy about this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Shiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about him. He's an advisor. So remonstrating is his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a quite fragile position right now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stake that sticks out gets hammered down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the three thousand men of the Godo Family will soon carry you on their shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any clothes you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I have to pick an outfit, I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you pick the one you want the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want all the clothes here equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I pick one, that means I have to give up everything else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. This isn't the only opportunity for you to shop in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something you want, I'll bring you here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. So today, you can pick the one you want to wear now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you one thing, though... We won't come here every day, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, do I look cute? Do I look good in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You look really good in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never worn such light, smooth clothes before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on ahead and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SIG-Sauer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like your Beretta, it's a 9mm, 15-shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is smaller, isn't it? You said she's never used a gun before, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look too bad. I'll try with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't come all the way here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to deliver a gun that I didn't even request, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl, Cal, was mentioned in today's meeting among the senior members.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Wisemel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's worse. It was McGwire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wants to see what progress she's making.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be better if you at least teach her how to use a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You've already changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Sunday clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are good enough to wear at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess. Those clothes will do fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to practice using a gun now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... the practice grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a lonely place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold the gun firmly. Focus your strength on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stretch your right arm and pull with your left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure your target can be seen through the gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands are shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus your strength on the fingers holding the gun instead of your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, keep holding it like that, and slowly pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were too hasty. Do it more slowly. Pull it as if you're squeezing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I hit the target! I hit the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that, Reiji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try changing the magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's very careful and good at handling the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Try practicing by yourself for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lonely place"...huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You talkin' to me? You talkin' to me? You talkin' to me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Then who the hell else are you talking... you talkin' to me? Okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're dead."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Oh duh... Missed big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... uhm... that was... well, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was doing De Niro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That De Niro or whatever. Do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You talkin to me? You talkin' to..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the dialogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. Don't shoot right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you have it at the ready, count to one before you shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit the target?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! I hit the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready to go shark fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Godo's sick and tired of staying put.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's planning to splurge and have fun tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mission is to keep an eye on them
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wait for Wisemel to slip up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.81,0:15:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My picks weren't even remotely close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! This isn't my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who believe in the Goddess of Victory can win her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already got her to spread her legs. I can't win her heart now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? You're quitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that doesn't betray me is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink too much, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be sticking with his group like other Japanese people, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiga, join me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Okay, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think a place like this is under the mafia's control?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. This isn't a De Niro movie, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is probably a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is it alright to make her take the same path as mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I shouldn't. I'll set her free... as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go play poker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think my friend was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a Japanese man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he went back to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was with a young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took the bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C... Can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed her... So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
